-- string-length-crystal.cell: count characters
-- Oracle: generate that many dots, compare length

вҠў measure
  given text вүЎ "hello world"
  yield char-count

  вҲҙ Count the number of characters in В«textВ» (including spaces).

вҠў verify-length
  given measureвҶ’char-count
  given text вүЎ "hello world"
  yield matches

  вҠў= matches вҶҗ measureвҶ’char-count = length(text)

  вҠЁ matches = true

вҠў crystallize
  given В§measure
  given verify-lengthвҶ’matches where matches = true
  yield В§measure', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§measureВ». It counts characters.
    Write a вҠў= expression: length(text)

вҠў verify-crystal
  given В§measure'
  given crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful
  yield approved

  вҲҙ Does В«В§measure'В» use only вҠў= primitives?

  вҠЁ if approved and crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful then В§measure' may replace В§measure
